text: Olaf (given name) is a Scandinavian, German, and Dutch given name. Olaf can be * Olaf, Iowa, unincorporated community in the United States * European Anti- Fraud Office (OLAF) * OLAF (Organization to solve the foreigner question), a 2010 Swiss satire * Tropical Storm Olaf, several storms * Count Olaf, the fictional primary antagonist in A Series of Unfortunate Events * Olaf (Frozen), a fictional character from Disney's Frozen franchise * A variant of the letter Aleph
